message.content: cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper introduces a dataset for evaluating automatic story comprehension from both video and text, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
